name: Guru Chicks Farms India Private Limited
description: suppliers of exclusive array of Chicken
overview:
Established in the year 2011 at Tirupur, Tamil Nadu in India,? Guru Chicks Farms India Private Limited is revered as one of the trusted?processors and suppliers of broad spread array of superior quality Poultry Feed Supplements, Chicken Eggs and Chicken Birds.

Products/; Chicken Birds Country Chicken Birds Broiler Chicks Brown Hens Battery Hens Broiler Chicken Birds Chicken Eggs Poultry Feed Supplements

Infrastructural Facilities: Guru Chicks Farm is well-equipped with state-of-the-art infrastructural facility that spread across acres of land area and is responsible of conducting entire processing as well as supplying with utmost precision.

Team of Experts: We are supported by expert team of professionals, who carry immense industrial experience in the field of Poultry farming and breeding. Our professionals are selected on the basis of their skills, knowledge and previous year’s experience. Besides, we conduct regular workshops and training to keep their efficiencies to the maximum and fully aware of customer’s demands and needs.

Client Satisfaction: Being involved in offering finest quality products to our clients, we have rendered high level of customer satisfaction. Our professionals work tirelessly hard to process the range that suits the taste and preferences of our clients.
